    "sections": {
        "description": "<p>When you have set Visibility settings in Beaver Builder, it&#8217;s not easy to see what rows, columns and modules appear on different devices. This plugin adds a visual guide with a click of a button.<\/p>\n",
        "faq": "\n<dt id='how%20does%20it%20work'>\nHow does it work\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>Beaver Builder lets you hide and show elements based on &#8220;Visibility&#8221; settings dependent on device size. You can control these via the &#8216;Advanced&#8217; tab in row, column and module settings in the &#8216;Visibility&#8217; section. Which is great, but the only problem is you can&#8217;t then see which elements are hiding and showing until you click on each of their settings.<\/p>\n<p>In order to see which modules, columns and rows are showing\/hiding, edit any page with Beaver Builder and you will see the &#8220;UI&#8221; button appear in the top bar. Click on that to see which elements you have with Visibility settings and which devices they are set to.<\/p>\n<\/p>\n\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.0.5<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tested for WP 6.4+ and edge cases added for separated responsive choices.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.4<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated for new responsive Extra Large breakpoint in Beaver Builder 2.6<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.3<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated compatibility for WP 5.9.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.2<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>jQuery updates for WP 5.7<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Amendments to styling so it is more obvious when it is on \/ off<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial Version<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
        "screenshots": "<ol><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/responsive-ui-for-beaver-builder\/assets\/screenshot-1.png?rev=2454796\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/responsive-ui-for-beaver-builder\/assets\/screenshot-1.png?rev=2454796\" alt=\"Once activated you will see the UI button appear in the top of Beaver Builder screenshot-1.png\"><\/a><p>Once activated you will see the UI button appear in the top of Beaver Builder screenshot-1.png<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/responsive-ui-for-beaver-builder\/assets\/screenshot-2.png?rev=2454796\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/responsive-ui-for-beaver-builder\/assets\/screenshot-2.png?rev=2454796\" alt=\"You will see different icons depending on which Breakpoints you have set in the Visibility settings screenshot-2.png\"><\/a><p>You will see different icons depending on which Breakpoints you have set in the Visibility settings screenshot-2.png<\/p><\/li><\/ol>",
        "reviews": "<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very handy!<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/hedley\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/fb45bfd4948d51489189108afa7bccb1?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/fb45bfd4948d51489189108afa7bccb1?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/hedley\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Hedley<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">January 10, 2024<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Much better visibility for responsive-specific components in the editor.  <\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">So simple...<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/deargeek\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/1f84e1fa2edbbe3f02e57631bf880103?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/1f84e1fa2edbbe3f02e57631bf880103?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/deargeek\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">deargeek<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 4, 2021<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">...yet so perfect.\n\nGreat idea, thank you!<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very Useful<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/molloy68\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/61b48d2b4d4c1d3477b96f9527212a99?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/61b48d2b4d4c1d3477b96f9527212a99?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/molloy68\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">molloy68<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">January 22, 2021<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">If you work with Beaver Builder you need this.  Especially if you design more than just a basic site.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Handy and easy to use<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/gdgraphics\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/a4afffdd84aa577cb8b728f0a70bdf65?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/a4afffdd84aa577cb8b728f0a70bdf65?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/gdgraphics\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">gdgraphics<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">January 22, 2021<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">It's one of those plugins that you didn't know you needed until you have used it. This plugin is essential for extensive users of Beaver Builder when creating websites for clients professionally.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">A very handy tool for Beaver Builder users<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/waumsley\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/af0585107d109af60003f5f6fc424a73?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/af0585107d109af60003f5f6fc424a73?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/waumsley\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">David Waumsley <small>(waumsley)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">January 17, 2021<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Thanks Chris for making this. It's going to be very useful on sites where I use Beaver Builder visibility a lot. It should stop me deleting those \"spacer\" columns I set up and later forget about - whoops!.\n\nPerfect as a plugin rather than as something in Beaver Builder.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n"
